Acceptance: Room requests reuse existing GitHub-originated runner/work-item semantics for isolation, runner selection, acknowledgement, cancellation, retry, progress, blocked, and completion. Background permission is separate, duplicate idempotency keys do not start duplicate work, and durable progress/results land in the anchored thread. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-12-github-item-room-routing.md.